(19, 1, '2024-02-12 23:31:24', '2024-02-12 23:31:24', 'Hi , I am Suvam Chauhan , a second year student of Georgian college studying Interactive Media Design - Web [IMDW]  program . Starting my journey in web design felt like stepping into a world where I had no experience and basic knowledge on Computer. In my first semester, I was captivated by the simplicity of HTML and CSS, shaping my first static websites with excitement. As the semesters progressed, I delved deeper into the intricacies of JavaScript, mastering its magic in bringing interactivity to my creations. With each project, I felt more confident, seamlessly blending responsive design principles and backend development techniques into my repertoire. Nowadays, I find this course very interesting and knowledgeable because of the  professors who are amazing and very helpful throughout my ongoing study. Till the last semester these are the things that I learned from this course.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Programming Languages: Python, JavaScript, C, C#, React</li>\r\n 	<li>Web Development: HTML, CSS</li>\r\n 	<li>Database Management: SQL</li>\r\n 	<li>Software Tools: Visual Studio Code, Photoshop, Illustrator\"</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;', 'My academic journey :', '', 'trash', 'open', 'open', '', 'my-academic-journey__trashed', '', '', '2024-03-31 23:54:09', '2024-03-31 23:54:09', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=19', 0, 'post', '', 0),
